title: Dog Harness No Pull Adjustable Reflective Step-in Soft Nylon For Small Large Pet TLH56512(XS, Blue)
seller_info_text: Truelove Pet Garment and Shoes Co.Ltd.
features: 1. Easy to adjust and put on. Four adjustable straps allow a custom fit for your dog.
2. Vibrant Color & nylon strip with 3M reflective improve visibility at night. Soft padded in chest and belly for comfortable.
3. Two attachment points for extra control. This harness attaches in the normal back/neck area and also under the stomach.
4. The handle on the back can help better control the movement of dog and for attaching safety belt.

5. Please measure your dog's chest measurement at the same place as the line. The recommended breast size will be 2 inches smaller than the product size on the label, which would provide space for adjustment. If your dog's chest is approaching maximum chest size, you can choose the next size.
description: Product Description TLH56512 Truelove Reflective high-end Dog Harness TLH56512 harness is available in ten bright colors and five sizes. Durable outer layer and soft mesh padded, scrath-resistant oxford material outer layer, lightweight soft sandwish mesh lining and soft sponge padded in chest and belly for good load dispersion and comfortable, extended wear. Strong tensile strength, double stitching and load capacity buckles allow this harness to hold back even strong pullers. Product description Easy on and off Light weight aluminum fittings on neck strap make the dog harness easier to put on and take off. Wearing position of LED light A navigation light can be hung on the back to ensure safe travel at night. Reflective webbing Reflective webbing ensures good visibility at night. Easy to adjust buckle Four buckles make the harness easy to adjust. Adjusting the size and comfort is also very important. It fits the dog's body shape and receives uniform force, which make the wrapping more comfortable. Up close position Made of thick nylon webbing, it is strong and resistant to pulling. It can better control the dog's movement and ensure safety when getting close to the dog. You can also wear the seat belt here to prevent the dog from running in the car. D-ring and Buckle Two-leash attachment points: light weight aluminum D-ring on the dog's back, and webbing with light weight aluminum O-ring on the dog's chest. Buckles are lightweight and have large loading capacity which improve the tensile strength of the dog harness. Find the Right Size (The following are the sizes for the dog's chest.) XS 11-15 in S 15-20 in M 20-25 in L 25-30 in XL 30-40 in It's very important to find the right size: Measure your dog's width/girth by wrapping a tape measure around your dog's chest, just behind the front legs. The chest size recommended will be 2 inches less than the product size in the size chart, which would provide some space for adjustment. If your dog's chest is approaching the max chest size, you may choose the next size up. Please refer to the size chart to choose the right size for your dog.
